title: Cream & Deep Purple - The Farewell Tour - Inglewood 68 - 2CD
description:
CREAM on their Farewell Tour - with supporting band DEEP PURPLE (Mark I) - at The L.A. Forum, Inglewood, CA in October 1968.


2 Disc


1 DEEP PURPLE    
 
  LIVE AT INGLEWOOD   1968

  - Official Archive Collection
  - CD
  - 2009
  - 320Kbps



2 CREAM

  THE FAREWELL TOUR   1968

  - Woodstock Tapes
  - CD
  - 2007
  - 320Kbps



Note:

DEEP PURPLE recorded at The L.A. Forum, Inglewood, CA on October 18th 1968

CREAM recorded at The L.A. Forum, Inglewood, CA on October 18th and 19th 1968, even though one or more tracks might come from the show in Oakland on October 4th - as some experts believe . . .


Anyway, enjoy . . .  ;)
